<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GoDoctor - Home Page</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset and base styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Hero section styles */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            padding-left: 2rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 100px;
        }

            .hero img {
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                object-fit: cover;
                z-index: -1;
                opacity: 0.7;
            }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            max-width: 600px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #0066cc; /* Changed from #e6f3ff to pure white for better visibility */
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Added text shadow for better contrast */
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #ffffff; /* Changed from #cce6ff to pure white for better visibility */
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Added text shadow for better contrast */
        }

        /* Button styles for both */
        .cta-btn, .hero-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #0066cc;
            padding: 1rem 3rem; /* Increase padding */
            font-size: 1.5rem; /* Larger font size */
            font-weight: 700; /* Bold text */
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Add box shadow */
        }

            .cta-btn:hover, .hero-btn:hover {
                background-color: #e6f3ff;
                transform: translateY(-3px);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            }

        /* Features section styles */
        .features {
            padding: 6rem 0;
            background-color: #e6f3ff;
        }

            .features h2 {
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                color: #0052a3;
                margin-bottom: 3rem;
            }

        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

            .feature-card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
                box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            }

            .feature-card h3 {
                color: #0066cc;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #0066cc;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* CTA section styles */
        .cta-section {
            background-color: #0066cc;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }

            .cta-section h2 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }

            .cta-section p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
                max-width: 800px;
                margin-left: auto;
                margin-right: auto;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <img src="~/Img/PagesImages/1.jpg" alt="Healthcare Image">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <div class="hero-text">
                    <h1>Discover Excellence in Healthcare</h1>
                    <p>Find your health haven at GoDoctor, where your well-being is our top priority. With personalized care and a commitment to excellence, we're here to support you on your journey to better health.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="hero-btn">Find a Doctor Now</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="features">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Why Choose GoDoctor?</h2>
                <div class="feature-grid">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">🔍</div>
                        <h3>Easy Search</h3>
                        <p>Find the right doctor with our advanced search options. Filter by specialty, location, and availability to get the care you need.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">📅</div>
                        <h3>Online Booking</h3>
                        <p>Book appointments instantly, 24/7 at your convenience. No more waiting on hold or playing phone tag.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">💻</div>
                        <h3>Virtual Consultations</h3>
                        <p>Connect with doctors remotely for follow-ups and minor issues. Save time and stay safe with our telemedicine options.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Ready to Take Control of Your Health?</h2>
                <p>Join thousands of satisfied patients who have found their perfect healthcare match with GoDoctor.</p>
                <a href="#" class="cta-btn">Sign Up Now</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
